: : CUSTOMS ORDINANCE: RESOLUTION ( ) (The Hon. Jeyaraj Fernandopulle) Sir, on behalf of the Hon. Prime Minister, Minister of Internal Administration, and Deputy Minister of Defence, Public Security, Law and Order, I move, That the resolution under Section 10 of the Customs Ordinance (Chapter 235) relating to import duties which was presented on 12-10-2007 be approved. , . . Question put, and agreed to.
. Adjourned accordingly at 1.26 p.m. until 9.30 a.m. on Tuesday, 6th November, 2007.
